snippet.title: Tony Hawk's Pro Skater 1 + 2 - Pre-Order Trailer - Nintendo Switch | E3 2021
snippet.description:
Get ready to spin, flip and grind through two iconic skateboarding games when Tony Hawk's Pro Skater 1 + 2 comes to Nintendo Switch on June 25. 

#THPS #NintendoSwitch #NintendoDirect

Pre-order today: https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/tony-hawks-pro-skater-1-and-2-switch/
